featured_reviews.review_id:
Mashallah nice mosque.
Second mosque of kumta Town located in Muslim galli,behind kumta juma mosque and markaz,
Difficult to reach here in four wheelers.
Big issue is their is not have parking space infront of this mosque even road is to narrow. Not visible from main road.
Juma time in both mosque is approximately same.
